        <Parent_String>color film (film, material) [300127339], photographic film (photographic materials) [300014638], photographic media [300430220], photographic materials [300127358], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
